{"tid":1564010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"再次有請阿寶","createTime":"2019-09-12T15:16:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T15:32:03.000Z","uid":276437,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e8daea273b4e5613dfc4063a1399cf581c059eef","tid":1564010,"uid":276437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:16:07.000Z","msg":"#阿寶好忙<br />\n轉貼自某fb page <br />\n<br />\n無論如何力挽狂瀾，都無法避免金鐘化。看這些人的嘴臉，以小人之心猜度人，就知道是無法勸服的。2019，雖不唱《今天我》，不舉黃傘，不叫階段性勝利，但一樣可以有新歌唱，有新旗舉，有新口號可以叫。<br />\n<br />\n他們不會想，為何唱，為何舉，為何叫，和勝利有何關係。正如當年，你罵人唱今天我，他們也會說要凝聚人心啊共鳴啊云云。凝聚人心了又如何勝利？他們回答不到。<br />\n<br />\n我知這幾日很多同道都很悲哀，和不少朋友吵到反面。眼見著金鐘重現，想力挽狂瀾，反過來被指責。彷彿又回到了以前，你無法叫醒裝睡的人。香港人一如以往，腳肯用力，都肯走出來食彈了，腦卻放假，了解一點政治都不肯。<br />\n<br />\n不要理會這些「放假腦」，我們專心做事，正如一直以來我們旗手也不多，行動亦人少，但堅持做有效的事，自自然然會有人加入。<br />\n<br />\n所以，輪到我們的腦放下假了，不要為他們勞氣，好好休息整頓，然後努力，互勉之。<br />\n<br />\n後記：今次又係叫我熱狗/分化撚定係對準政權 ？<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rQ9eGzm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrQ9eGzm.jpg&h=70a5fbd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"083b0c7ed57a602a9d8ec90a52a4158fc2e5f7d2","tid":1564010,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:16:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"fb7db51efd003fb159380d6cb5b3677780a32d20","tid":1564010,"uid":276437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:20:52.000Z","msg":"再談<br />\n其實依家最唔撚民主嘅就係泛民<br />\n一有意見不合/批評就屌鳩你分化熱狗<br />\n連少少討論同批評嘅空間都唔容許仲講乜撚嘢民主<br />\n呢班仆街同一黨專政嘅共產黨有乜撚野分別"},{"pid":"bf14c80bdef87ed74b8ca8957e539c1bbde15698","tid":1564010,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgsafe.org/a5/a5c603334c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgsafe.org%2Fa5%2Fa5c603334c.jpeg&h=b13a8b01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfd965387e5257c7c78ee4dea5ca6ef883c47452","tid":1564010,"uid":59408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T15:32:03.000Z","msg":"完全冇思考過香港人真正想點<br />\n要一個點嘅獨立調查委員會<br />\n要一個點嘅真普選<br />\n要一套點嘅提名原則<br />\n等等"}]}